<Content>As above This is a case where we are all in agreement. Very basic, quite cheap. Staff comically unhelpful and unknowledgable.Good place for quick stop rather than lengthy stay. Bring mosquito repellant. We are not kidding.There is a dreadful underpass you have to walk through (because there is no bus nearby) HOWEVER rail station is very close and great for Florence, Lucca and all points.The tower and Campo de Miracoli are great though and make up for it. 
